'''T'iil''' was a fragrant [[Alderaan/Legends|Alderaanian]] [[Flower/Legends|flowering]] [[Plant/Legends|plant]]. The flower itself was shaped like a trumpet, and bloomed with a vibrant yellow color. On [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]], [[Shaak/Legends|shaaks]] and other large herd animals helped pollinate the t'iil.<ref name="Frontier" />

The extract from the white core of the plant's roots was considered a treatment for sore throats. The leaves of the plant were used to create a soothing tea. The single drop of nectar found in the t'iil was harvested and used to distill [[l'lahsh]].<ref name="Frontier" />

The [[T'iil seed cake]] was eaten in the [[Royal Palace of Alderaan/Legends|Aldera Royal Palace]] during the [[Imperial Era/Legends|Imperial Period]], and the [[T'iil Blossom Homes]] building on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Delaya/Legends|Delaya]] housed Alderaanian refugees after the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] [[Destruction of Alderaan/Legends|destroyed]] Alderaan.<ref name="Hostage">''[[Rebel Force: Hostage]]''</ref>

